<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>You can close these dialogs just by pressing Escape;</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="07371d37-6fef-4945-9da7-ac3b15af69c8">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 32</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>You can assign a shortcut to open these dialogs in "Input gestures" menu and, more precisely, in the "Day of the week" category;</source>
</segment>
</unit>
